                Papiae <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Maximae <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Agrius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Fortunatus <lb n="5"/>IIIIIIvir coniu<lb break="no" n="6"/>gi <expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erenti</ex></expan> et suis <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in Wiederverwendung als Abdeckplatte für einen römischen Abwasserkanal, der vom Hügel herab zum Fluß führte.</p>
